New Connect REST API Resource in Record Rollup Definitions

Get record rollup results for a specific record aggregation definition.
Make a POST request to the new /connect/record-aggregation/recordAggregationDefinitionId/record-rollup-results resource.
New request body: Record Rollup Input
New response body: Record Rollup
